WEBVTT

00:00:17.297 --> 00:00:18.285
Uh...

00:00:18.286 --> 00:00:20.354
I'm sorry...

00:00:21.001 --> 00:00:23.991
Sorry, sorry!

00:00:26.649 --> 00:00:29.162
It's fine, just go wash up.

00:00:29.824 --> 00:00:32.133
Okay...

00:00:39.279 --> 00:00:43.863
(Visual Design) (Industrial
Design) (Media Design)

00:00:45.300 --> 00:00:47.779
And Architectural Design too.

00:00:47.780 --> 00:00:50.029
There are all kinds of
different design fields,

00:00:50.030 --> 00:00:51.649
but for today's class,

00:00:51.650 --> 00:00:53.120
we'll only be covering...

00:00:53.121 --> 00:00:54.253
Is everything okay?

00:00:54.254 --> 00:00:55.721
What?

00:00:55.722 --> 00:00:56.930
No...

00:01:08.869 --> 00:01:12.389
[Your request to return has been denied. What
are you doing in the human world right now?

00:01:17.264 --> 00:01:20.155
If you want to come back, stop
letting humans sway you. At this rate,

00:01:20.179 --> 00:01:22.903
you really could get trapped
there. I'll file an appeal for now.]

00:01:48.803 --> 00:01:50.149
Huh?

00:01:50.150 --> 00:01:51.789
Why'd class end so late?

00:01:51.790 --> 00:01:53.289
Something happen?

00:01:53.290 --> 00:01:54.539
Nothing really.

00:01:54.540 --> 00:01:56.061
What are you up to now?

00:01:56.062 --> 00:01:57.530
Nothing, really.

00:01:57.531 --> 00:02:00.220
Then come help me train.

00:02:01.568 --> 00:02:02.449
Me too?

00:02:02.450 --> 00:02:03.809
Yeah.

00:02:03.810 --> 00:02:04.929
Think of it as working out

00:02:04.930 --> 00:02:06.572
I'll teach you some self-defense.

00:02:06.573 --> 00:02:07.689
What if I don't want to?

00:02:07.690 --> 00:02:10.519
Then I'll just take Jihan with me.

00:02:10.520 --> 00:02:11.809
You're coming with me, right?

00:02:11.810 --> 00:02:15.409
Uh... yeah.

00:02:15.410 --> 00:02:17.537
Let's go, let's go, let's go.

00:02:20.399 --> 00:02:25.111
[Lecture Hall]

00:02:27.500 --> 00:02:29.737
Hyunjun helps me train pretty often.

00:02:29.738 --> 00:02:31.618
Ohhh...

00:02:32.659 --> 00:02:35.139
Oh, want me to lend you a training uniform?

00:02:35.140 --> 00:02:37.931
Mm... I'm okay.

00:02:46.034 --> 00:02:47.361
What's wrong?

00:02:47.362 --> 00:02:48.087
Huh?

00:02:48.088 --> 00:02:49.318
You okay?

00:02:49.319 --> 00:02:51.104
Uh... yeah, I'm fine.

00:02:51.105 --> 00:02:52.229
You're not hurt or anything?

00:02:52.230 --> 00:02:54.719
I... I'm really...

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:56.375
really okay...

00:02:56.376 --> 00:02:58.376
Alright then.

00:03:07.555 --> 00:03:09.883
Okay, let's start with stretching.

00:03:09.884 --> 00:03:10.704
Okay.

00:03:10.705 --> 00:03:12.860
Put your legs together.

00:03:13.387 --> 00:03:16.962
Now bend forward nice and slow.

00:03:19.368 --> 00:03:23.582
- Stretch, stretch, stretch.
- Ah... ah... ahh!!

00:03:23.583 --> 00:03:26.478
Loosen up your back too.

00:03:27.810 --> 00:03:30.610
Other side now.

00:03:33.789 --> 00:03:35.553
Are you good at splits?

00:03:35.554 --> 00:03:37.119
I've never tried...

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:38.824
Let's find out.

00:03:38.825 --> 00:03:40.825
Spread your legs!

00:03:42.597 --> 00:03:44.658
Your hands!

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:48.028
Alright, I'm pulling now, okay?

00:03:48.336 --> 00:03:49.260
Streeetch.

00:03:49.261 --> 00:03:50.829
Ahh wait wait wait!

00:03:50.830 --> 00:03:53.866
Ahhh seriously seriously, hold on!!

00:03:53.867 --> 00:03:54.750
More! More!

00:03:54.750 --> 00:03:55.340
No no no no!

00:03:55.341 --> 00:03:56.789
You can do it, you can do it!

00:03:56.790 --> 00:03:58.169
- Streeetch.
- Seriously!!

00:03:58.170 --> 00:04:00.767
Streeetch!

00:04:46.594 --> 00:04:48.549
I can't breathe...

00:04:48.550 --> 00:04:51.491
Uh... sorry sorry sorry!

00:04:53.200 --> 00:04:56.389
Alright, wanna start for real now?

00:04:56.390 --> 00:04:57.925
Yeah!

00:04:57.926 --> 00:04:59.926
Give me your hand.

00:05:04.712 --> 00:05:06.873
Think you can copy this?

00:05:08.162 --> 00:05:10.309
Yeah!

00:05:10.310 --> 00:05:12.310
Go for it.

00:05:19.282 --> 00:05:22.648
Uh... Kang Jihan! Kang Jihan, let go!

00:05:22.649 --> 00:05:25.217
Hey, let go of my hand! Get down, get down!

00:05:25.218 --> 00:05:26.513
Did I do good?

00:05:26.514 --> 00:05:29.162
Hey, okay okay... hold on!

00:05:30.876 --> 00:05:34.139
Alright, should we move on to the next one?

00:05:34.140 --> 00:05:35.801
Sounds good.

00:05:35.802 --> 00:05:38.137
This time it's a takedown move.

00:05:38.138 --> 00:05:40.059
Grab your opponent by the chest,

00:05:40.060 --> 00:05:43.610
hook their leg, and...

00:05:44.197 --> 00:05:45.979
Harder than it looks, right?

00:05:45.980 --> 00:05:47.446
Yeah.

00:05:47.447 --> 00:05:48.759
Try throwing me.

00:05:48.760 --> 00:05:51.270
If you manage it today,
I'll grant you one wish.

00:05:51.271 --> 00:05:52.319
Seriously?

00:05:52.320 --> 00:05:55.749
You better not take that back later.

00:05:55.750 --> 00:05:58.458
'Cause I won't go easy on you this time.

00:06:03.130 --> 00:06:06.386
Nah, again.

00:06:08.020 --> 00:06:10.570
Come at me!

00:06:12.270 --> 00:06:14.469
That's not how you do it.

00:06:14.470 --> 00:06:15.739
Try again, try again.

00:06:15.740 --> 00:06:17.677
Again, again.

00:06:17.678 --> 00:06:18.950
Hey!

00:06:18.951 --> 00:06:21.320
That's cheating!

00:06:21.321 --> 00:06:23.321
There you go!

00:06:24.325 --> 00:06:25.898
I don't think you can...

00:06:25.899 --> 00:06:28.442
Guess I can't grant your wish after all.

00:06:29.283 --> 00:06:32.359
Uh... what?

00:06:33.400 --> 00:06:36.499
Jihan isn't actually a
student at our school?

00:06:36.500 --> 00:06:38.130
Yeah

00:06:38.131 --> 00:06:40.319
I asked the professor in
charge of the freshmen,

00:06:40.320 --> 00:06:42.901
and he had no idea who he was.

00:06:42.902 --> 00:06:45.449
At first I thought maybe
he was just forgettable,

00:06:45.450 --> 00:06:48.219
so I asked some freshmen too...

00:06:48.220 --> 00:06:49.969
but nobody knew him.

00:06:49.970 --> 00:06:52.949
No clue how he even ended up here...

00:06:52.950 --> 00:06:55.269
Honestly, something felt
off about him from the start.

00:06:55.270 --> 00:06:56.769
He kept saying weird stuff.

00:06:56.770 --> 00:06:58.159
Weird stuff?

00:06:58.160 --> 00:07:00.326
Ah, when you asked before,

00:07:00.327 --> 00:07:03.209
I didn't really say anything,

00:07:04.010 --> 00:07:05.819
but the first time we met,

00:07:05.820 --> 00:07:07.199
he was talking about

00:07:07.200 --> 00:07:10.089
taking me somewhere
and all kinds of creepy stuff.

00:07:10.090 --> 00:07:14.801
Anyway, I don't think he's normal.

00:07:37.458 --> 00:07:39.682
Try getting out of this too.

00:07:39.683 --> 00:07:40.680
Ah, wait a second.

00:07:40.681 --> 00:07:42.822
Hard, right?

00:07:42.823 --> 00:07:44.138
Come here!

00:07:44.827 --> 00:07:48.094
[Poster reminding gym-goers
to maintain basic decency/hygiene]

00:07:49.860 --> 00:07:52.419
See? Not easy, right?

00:07:52.420 --> 00:07:54.580
Man, I shouldn't have come...

00:07:54.581 --> 00:07:55.921
What?

00:07:55.922 --> 00:07:58.345
Hey, now you're hurting my feelings

00:07:58.346 --> 00:08:01.848
I'm kidding.

00:08:01.849 --> 00:08:03.341
It was really fun.

00:08:03.342 --> 00:08:06.479
Right? It was fun, wasn't it?

00:08:09.889 --> 00:08:11.869
What? You leaving?

00:08:11.870 --> 00:08:14.659
Yeah, aren't you?

00:08:14.660 --> 00:08:17.209
I'm gonna train a little
more before I head out.

00:08:17.210 --> 00:08:19.927
Oh wait.

00:08:21.420 --> 00:08:23.109
Drink this.

00:08:23.110 --> 00:08:25.869
Oh, thanks.

00:08:25.870 --> 00:08:27.319
Then I'll get going first.

00:08:27.320 --> 00:08:29.382
Get home safe.

00:08:39.820 --> 00:08:44.076
Ugh... ha...

00:08:44.077 --> 00:08:47.593
This is really not the time for this...

00:08:58.814 --> 00:09:01.514
Hey there.

00:09:04.020 --> 00:09:05.737
This belongs to you, right?

00:09:05.738 --> 00:09:07.738
The death ledger.

00:09:11.710 --> 00:09:15.128
You can't go back anymore.

00:09:28.735 --> 00:09:31.669
Why are you here
when you're not even in our department?

00:09:31.670 --> 00:09:35.349
I'm here to ask Jihan to revise the logo.

00:09:35.350 --> 00:09:35.980
Get out already.

00:09:35.981 --> 00:09:38.918
We don't allow sweaty outsiders in here.

00:09:38.919 --> 00:09:40.619
Sweaty?

00:09:40.620 --> 00:09:42.235
Then why the hell are you always here?

00:09:42.236 --> 00:09:44.236
Me?

00:09:44.620 --> 00:09:46.649
Oh, you're here?

00:09:46.650 --> 00:09:48.742
Come here.

00:09:50.723 --> 00:09:51.509
What are you doing?

00:09:51.510 --> 00:09:52.569
What are you doing?

00:09:52.570 --> 00:09:53.913
Jihan is sitting next to me.

00:09:53.914 --> 00:09:55.189
No, he's sitting next to me.

00:09:55.190 --> 00:09:58.564
Uh... I should probably get going first.

00:09:59.640 --> 00:10:01.689
He left because of the
way you were glaring at him.

00:10:01.690 --> 00:10:03.139
No, he left because you smell sweaty.

00:10:03.140 --> 00:10:05.140
What?

00:10:05.800 --> 00:10:08.800
"Fix the Error!"